[[File:KDT.jpg|thumb|right|280px|A [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|BTL Y-wing starfighter]] attacks [[Sentinel-class landing craft/Legends|''Sentinel''-class landing crafts]] of KDT Group.]]
'''KDT''' was the designation of a convoy of [[Sentinel-class landing craft/Legends|''Sentinel''-class landing craft]] carrying [[Prisoner/Legends|prisoners]] and supplies. It was overseen by [[Imperial II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial II''-class Star Destroyer]] [[Goliath (Imperial II-class)|''Goliath'']].

Several of them had [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]] who were sympathetic to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] cause.

After a mysterious transmission by an unnamed [[Zaletta|informer]], four [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wings]]&mdash;one of them piloted by [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen]]&mdash;and three [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|T-65 X-wing starfighters]] attacked the convoy and disabled the convoy craft with the slaves near the [[Golan I Space Defense Platform/Legends|Golan platform]] [[Golan I (space station)|Golan I]]. Then [[Gamma-class ATR-6 assault transport|''Gamma''-class ATR-6 assault transports]] from [[Tango Group|Tango squadron]] liberated the slaves while the Rebel fighters provided cover for them.

